    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a5 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 37px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">га </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Манзил:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс номи ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">томонидан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">(даъво предметини ўзгартириш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бераман ушбу аризани шу ҳақдаким, мен иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">судига жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича жавобгар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ҳақидаги даъво ариза билан мурожаат қилганман. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ҳозирда жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича жавобгар ташкилотнинг ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли ва номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> мен билан келишган ҳолда </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Иш бўйича жавобгар ихтиёрий равишда қаноатлантирган даъво талаблари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> тўғрисидаги даъво талабимни ихтиёрий равишда қаноатлантирди. </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Иш бўйича жавобгар томонидан ихтиёрий равишда қаноатлантирилмаган (ҳозир ҳам мавжуд бўлган) низолар бўйича даъво талаблари</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> тўғрисидаги даъво талабим бўйича ҳозир ҳам низо мавжуд.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шу сабабли мен Ўзбекистон Республикаси ИПКнинг 41, 43-моддаларига асосан билдирилган талабларнинг предметига ўзгартириш киритиб, фақатгина </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Иш бўйича жавобгар томонидан ихтиёрий равишда қаноатлантирилмаган (ҳозир ҳам мавжуд бўлган) низолар бўйича даъво талаблари </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">тўғрисидаги даъво талабимни қонуний кўриб чиқиб, қарор қабул қилишингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ариза берувчи юридик шахс раҳбарининг ёки якка тартибдаги тадбиркор (ЯТТ)нинг Ф.И.Оси</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">имзо</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-top: 2pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
